 ideal, and with a drop in class, she is ready to win. 10. HELLABELLA has looked good in this campaign. She just missed fresh at Wyong, then used her speed to full effect when leading throughout for a tough maiden win over this distance at Rosehill 9 days ago. Tim Clark sticks with her, and so do we. 5. SURF'S UP went around as the favourite first-up at Randwick-Kensington, but after trailing a small field into the straight, she could only manage fourth. She showed a stack of promise in the spring, and she will be a sharp improver in this. JMac sticks, so follow your money. 4. JUST GLAMOUROUS resumes after 5 months off. He comes to hand quickly, and she will only need a genuine tempo up front for her to be a top 4 hope. Watch for her late.\",\"runners\":[2,10,5,4],\"exclusive\":true}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Darren Flindell","tipRunnerNumbers":[11,10,5,2]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,11,10,9]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,9,3,4]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,11,2,10]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,3,10,9]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[10,5,3,4]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,9,12,11]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,2,10,9]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"WFM","raceType":"R"}}